original: Leffler, Dagny Margareta, tandläkare, Skara, f. 6/7/06 i Hästveda, Krist. 1., av Måns Niklasson o. Nelly Christenson. G. 35 m. tandl. Sven Leffler. Barn: Sven f. 35, Kerstin 38, Cecilia 46. — Stud:ex. i Lund 26, Cand. med. dent. i Greifswald 29, tysk tandl. där 31, sv. tandl. 32. Praktik i Tomelilla 33-35, i Skara sed. 36.
translated: Leffler, Dagny Margareta, dentist, Skara, born on 6th July 1906 in Hästveda, Kristianstad County, to parents Måns Niklasson and Nelly Christenson. Married in 1935 to dentist Sven Leffler. Children: Sven, born in 1935, Kerstin in 1938, Cecilia in 1946. Completed high school in Lund in 1926, obtained a dental degree (Cand. med. dent.) in Greifswald in 1929, practiced as a German dentist there in 1931 and as a Swedish dentist in 1932. Worked as an intern in Tomelilla from 1933 to 1935, and in Skara since 1936.
